{"title":"Programmer's Day","uid":"d68f216c2ae780f2cd7f0e97ab97b2a7","slug":"Personal blog","date":"2021-10-31T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2021-11-14T17:33:46.404Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Personal blog.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://destinyisto.github.io/post/background.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"My-blog\"><a href=\"#My-blog\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"My blog\"></a>My blog</h1><ul>\n<li>安装<strong>Git</strong>和<strong>Node.js</strong></li>\n<li>安装<strong>Hexo</strong></li>\n<li>加载主题</li>\n<li>修改配置</li>\n<li>部署博客</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"1-安装Git和Nodejs\"><a href=\"#1-安装Git和Nodejs\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.安装Git和Nodejs\"></a>1.安装Git和Nodejs</h2><ul>\n<li>访问<a href=\"https://git-scm.com/downloads\">Git</a>,点击<strong>Download for Windows</strong>，下载<strong>Git</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>打开<strong>Git Bash</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>依次输入下面俩行命令</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">git config --global user.name “Your Name”\ngit config --global user.email email@example.com\n# 其中Your Name和email@example.com替换成上面注册时的账户名和邮箱<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>访问<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/download\">Node.js</a>，点击<strong>Windows Installer</strong>，下载<strong>Node.js</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>依次输入以下命令查看是否安装成功</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">git version\nnode -v\nnpm -v<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"2-安装Hexo\"><a href=\"#2-安装Hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.安装Hexo\"></a>2.安装<strong>Hexo</strong></h2><ul>\n<li>输入以下命令</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">npm install -g hexo-cli<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>在指定文件夹下打开<strong>Git Bash</strong>，输入以下命令</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">hexo init myBlog\ncd myBlog \nnpm install<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>执行<code>hexo s</code>，在浏览器中访问<a href=\"http://localhost:4000/\">localhost:4000</a>,回车预览效果</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-加载主题\"><a href=\"#3-加载主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.加载主题\"></a>3.加载主题</h2><ul>\n<li><p>访问<a href=\"https://hexo.io/themes/\">Hexo</a>选择喜欢的主题进行下载</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>将下载的主题文件放在<code>myblog/themes</code>中，在<code>_config.yml</code>文件中修改<strong>theme</strong>为主题文件名</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在<strong>Git Bash</strong>执行<code>hexo g</code>，然后执行<code>hexo s</code>，在浏览器中访问<a href=\"http://localhost:4000/\">localhost:4000</a>，预览主题</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"4-修改配置\"><a href=\"#4-修改配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.修改配置\"></a>4.修改配置</h2><ul>\n<li>修改主题文件夹下的_config.yml文件，完成个人配置</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"5-部署博客\"><a href=\"#5-部署博客\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.部署博客\"></a>5.部署博客</h2><ul>\n<li><p>点击 <strong>Start project</strong> 或者下面的 <strong>new repository</strong> 建立一个新的仓库，注意<strong>Github</strong>仅能使用一个同名仓库的代码托管一个静态站点，这里注意仓库名一定要是：<code>用户名.github.io</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>配置 <strong>SSH key</strong> ，输入以下命令</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">git config --global user.name &quot;用户名&quot;\ngit config --global user.email &quot;邮箱地址&quot;\nssh-keygen -t rsa -C &#39;上面的邮箱&#39;<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li><p>输入命令<code>cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub </code>查看自己的 <strong>ssh</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>输入命令<code>ssh -T git@github.com</code>，若返回 <code>Hi xxx! You&#39;ve successfullyauthenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.</code>则添加成功</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>登陆 <strong>Github</strong> 上添加刚刚生成的 <strong>SSH key</strong>，按如下步骤，右上角点击<strong>头像</strong>-&gt; <strong>settings</strong> -&gt; <strong>SSH and GPG keys</strong>，建立一个新的 <strong>SSH key</strong>, <strong>key</strong> 就填写刚生成的<strong>ssh</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>第二要安装一个部署插件 <code>hexo-deployer-git</code>，打开 <strong>Git Bach</strong> ，输如以下命令</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>执行以下命令将个人博客部署上传</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">hexo g \t\t\t# 生成 generate \nhexo d \t\t\t# 部署 deploy<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>浏览器输入 <code>用户名.github.io</code> 进行访问</li>\n</ul>\n<img src=\"background.jpg\" alt=\"background\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" />\n\n\n\n","feature":true,"text":"My blog 安装Git和Node.js 安装Hexo 加载主题 修改配置 部署博客 1.安装Git和Nodejs 访问Git,点击Download for Windows，下载Git 打开Git Bash 依次输入下面俩行命令 git config --global user...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.4k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Programmer","slug":"Programmer","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Programmer.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Programmer's Day","slug":"Programmer-s-Day","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Programmer-s-Day.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#My-blog\"><span class=\"toc-text\">My blog</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Git%E5%92%8CNodejs\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.安装Git和Nodejs</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Hexo\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.安装Hexo</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E5%8A%A0%E8%BD%BD%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.加载主题</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\